name: BusinessJumper
overview:
BusinessJumper is an innovative educational service that allows people to take free live online classes and start their online business today.

The only cost for the class is the price of the offer that the person needs to complete in order to enroll. BusinessJumper selects the required services offered with a class so that the service is highly relevant to the subject taught. For example, in order to enroll into the “Start Your Own Personal Blog” class, you need to sign up for web hosting which you’re going to need afterwards to host your blog. After a short sign-process, you can enroll in any of the available classes listed on the website. Then you will be able to see the required offers to complete in order to take the class.
